improved_metadata.title: Whiskey Keys & Cowboy Regrets
improved_metadata.description: A melancholic song about heartbreak and regret, played out on a whiskey-soaked piano in a dimly lit bar. The lyrics explore the pain of past mistakes and the search for solace in music.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Whiskey keys, they play my pain, every know the drop of rain
